"title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_2287292","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"https://plus.google.com/108532847957327977828","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":19698089,"talkid":76945,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/387753.html?thread=19698089#t19698089","upictitle":"Tane Aikman: pic#0","article":"Finished the World book last night- thanks so much! Bliss for geeks like me who love getting all the detail of imaginary worlds. One thing: there was nothing about Great Moraq or the ports near Qarth. I know there were areas where you were deliberately vague, like Summerhall, because we will be learning more in the stories. Was that reason for the lack of detail about that area, or do you just not have much to say about it? I do hope we get to find out more either in the books or in an updated history.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 years ago","ctime":"November 3 2014, 08:28:54 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Wonderful! ","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"https://plus.google.com/108532847957327977828","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/google-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Tane Aikman","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_2287292","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=67558694&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Tane Aikman","ctime_ts":1415003334,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/124483323/36582828","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/387753.html?thread=19698601#t19698601","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/387753.html?thread=19698601#t19698601","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/387753.html?thread=19698601#t19698601","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"insurrbution","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://insurrbution.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":19698601,"talkid":76947,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/387753.html?thread=19698601#t19698601","upictitle":"insurrbution: pic#124483323","article":"Congrats George! Great stuff! The worldbook is prety awesome so far - I have no problem with Elio & Linda working with you on that book. It says so on the book itself, and you have mentioned it several times throughout your posts, so I knew beforehand. I believe that, as well as 'Lands of Ice and Fire' are the ultimate companions to the main books themselves. <br /><br />As for The Ice Dragon - I read it about two years ago (clearly not the new edition) and thought it's a great little 'bonus' whether or not it is related to The Seven Kingdoms. If yes, I can see Old Nan reading it to the Stark kids when they were babes. <br />I also think it would make a fantastic animated film... ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 years ago","ctime":"November 3 2014, 15:02:52 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://insurrbution.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"insurrbution","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"insurrbution","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://insurrbution.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"insurrbution","ctime_ts":1415026972,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/91237832/7059164","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/387753.html?thread=19699369#t19699369","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/387753.html?thread=19699369#t19699369","name":"colla